'''Stefanos Pavlakis''' (yavutse 1974), ni umukinnyi n'umwanditsi  wa filimi ukomoka mu [[Bugereki]]. <ref name="Stefanos">https://www.stefanos-pavlakis.com/person/</ref> <ref>https://www.behance.net/stefanospavlakis</ref> Yagize uruhare runini muri sinema ya Bénin akora documentaire zizwi cyane,''The Eye of the Beholder'', ''Studio Harmattan'' and ''Drive Through''<ref>https://www.beyondstorytelling.com/contributors-and-workshops/2016/10/5/stefanos-pavlakis</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Muri 2003, yarangije impamyabumenyi ya BA muri Film & Photography muri kaminuza ya Edinburgh Napier <ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Stefanos_Pavlakis</ref>. Hanyuma muri 2005, yarangije MFA nyuma aza kubona Ph.D.  muri kaminuza ya Dundee, Duncan of Jordanstone College of Art and Design .  <ref>https://kraft-des-zweifelns.de/de/1145-2/stefanos-pavlakis/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu mwaka wa 2009, yatangiye gukorana n’amasosiyete abiri akorera mu mujyi wa Berlin 'Expedere', 'Uruganda rw’Inkuru' maze akora documentaire ngufi, amatangazo n'ibikorwa byerekana. <ref>https://independent.academia.edu/StefanosPavlakis/CurriculumVitae</ref><ref>https://www.beyondstorytelling.com/contributors-and-workshops/2016/10/5/stefanos-pavlakis</ref>

